-- Vivendi Refinances $1.3 Billion Credit Line Maturing in 2011 With 10 Banks
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-23T06:07:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/vivendi-refinances-1-3-billion-credit-line-maturing-in-2011-with-10-banks.html

          
          
              Vivendi SA said it refinanced a 1
billion-euro credit line maturing in February 2011.  
 The new credit line will last until September 2015, the
company said in an emailed statement. Ten banks took part in the
refinancing, it said.  
          
          


  


        